*Znati* da je život kratak (To know that life is short).

*Znala* sam da ćeš doći (I knew that you would come).

Često *znaju* da se obmanu (They often deceive themselves).

*Znam* da je to teško (I know that it is difficult).

Oni *znaju* da se bore za pravdu (They know how to fight for justice).

Ona bi volela da ga *znaju* (She would like them to know him).

*Znale* smo da će doći (We knew they were coming).

*Znalo* se da je bio dobar čovek (It was known that he was a good man).